      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The corners were populated by the usual cast of characters: hardened figures leaning against boarded-up storefronts, their eyes darting like trapped animals. There were groups of young men, their clothing worn and their posture aggressive, moving with a coiled, restless energy. A few older residents shuffled by, their faces etched with the permanent weariness of surviving in this environment. They all moved with a shared, unspoken caution, making the sidewalk feel less like a path and more like a minefield.",
